{"id":74,"date":"2016-08-12T12:12:00","date_gmt":"2016-08-12T10:12:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/lyricalarabdance.it\/?p=74"},"modified":"2018-02-12T16:48:34","modified_gmt":"2018-02-12T15:48:34","slug":"residencial-workshops","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/lyricalarabdance.it\/2016\/08\/12\/residencial-workshops\/","title":{"rendered":"Residential summer workshop"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2>Lyrical Arab Dance residential summer workshop from July, 27th\/31th 2018<\/h2>\n<p>Join Sabina Todaro\u2019s Lyrical Arab dance workshop in P\u00e4rnu, Estonia.<br \/>\nIn P\u00e4rnu you can find both the seaside (with a beautiful sandy beach) and the atmosphere of a historical old\u00a0town with handicraft shops, little boutiques, lovely summer terraces and\u00a0nice restaurants. P\u00e4rnu is the summer capital of Estonia.<br \/>\nThe workshop will take place in Viiking Spa hotel, close to the beach\u00a0and the town center. Dance classes will be held daily in the wide\u00a0Victoria hall at the top floor of the hotel.<br \/>\nBetween dance classes you can\u00a0enjoy services of renewed spa department of the Viiking Spa hotel.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">WHEN:\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Travelling dates and workshop hours:\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fri 27.7. at 17-18.30 (1,5 h), travelling day\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sat 28.7. &#8211;\u00a0 Tue 31.7.\u00a0 at 10-13 (3 h, Group 1)\u00a0 and at 15-18 (3 h,\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Group 2)\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Wed 1.8. travelling day, no classes\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can choose as many dance classes as you\u00a0wish:\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TRAVEL BOOKING:\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Every participant will book their trip and accomodation by themselves.\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can make your travel booking through a travel agency called\u00a0Ikaalisten matkatoimisto.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We remind you that the change of July and August is the high season of traveling to P\u00e4rnu,\u00a0so travel booking ought to be done well in advance.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">STUDENTS:\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The workshop is for dancers of all levels, including beginners. No\u00a0previous knowledge is needed. Sabina\u2019s exercises are suitable for all\u00a0dancers regardless of their skill level. People who have practised\u00a0Pilates, Alexander Technique, Yoga or Martial Arts may find familiar\u00a0elements in Lyrical Arab Dance.\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">YOU ARE WARMLY WELCOME!\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u201dDance means joy, well-being, communication and love of life. It is a\u00a0willingness to share and celebrate, to be together in the moment,\u00a0recognizing ourselves in our humanity. Through dance we intend to\u00a0express the core of humanity from heart to heart.\u201d \u2013 Sabina Todaro\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u201dSabina\u2019s method encourages dancing and expression and time after time\u00a0makes a student find the joy of dance.\u201d \u2013 Taina\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u201dSabina builds dance movements through stretching and exercises. She is\u00a0a demanding teacher who has the ability to encourage and support her\u00a0students. In Lyrical Arab dance you can find the balance between body\u00a0and mind, leaving you with joy and longing for the next time.\u201d &#8211; Liisa\u00a0<\/span>2th to 7th August 2017 in the nice and charming\u00a0P\u00e4rnu, Estonian\u00a0summer capital!<\/p>\n<p>5 days dedicated to Lyrical Arab Dance, holyday\u00a0and well-being, in Estonia, where it is warm but not too much \ud83d\ude09<br \/>\nEvery day you can attend\u00a0up to 7 hours dance classes\u00a0or even only one so you have free time to dedicate\u00a0to rest and self-care.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_33\" style=\"width: 678px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><a href=\"http:\/\/lyricalarabdance.milangotan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2015\/05\/vacanza-studio-danza-in-estonia-300x200.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox-image-0\" data-rl_title=\"\" data-rl_caption=\"\" title=\"\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-33\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-33\" src=\"http:\/\/lyricalarabdance.milangotan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2015\/05\/vacanza-studio-danza-in-estonia-300x200-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"vacanza studio danza in Estonia\" width=\"668\" height=\"445\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-33\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dance trip\u00a0to Estonia<\/p><\/div>\n<p>We will stay at the Spa Hotel Viiking, located along the beach and equipped with a wellness center, beauty salon and spa.<br \/>\nThe dance classes are held in a large, bright and charming \u00a0top roof\u00a0Victoria Studio in the\u00a0hotel, in a pleasant atmosphere, helping\u00a0concentration, learning and training without any stress, promoting\u00a0serenity and joy of living.<br \/>\nYou can visit the website of Viiking: www.viiking.ee\/en<\/p>\n<p>Sabina Todaro uses a particular educational approach developed during her more than 25 years experience of teaching, which starts from the study of anatomy and neurology especially to get a central reinforcement of the body structure to improve efficiency, through a tonic and effective training. Once the body is awakened with various stretching exercises, balance and toning, Sabina accompanies students in search of their expressiveness and their own natural movement, directing them to the archaic language of the dance forms of the Arab world reinterpreted in a contemporary way.<br \/>\nAfter the class, you will feel that you have worked hard, but without exhaustion: people have an incredible positive life energy that takes them every day towards a feeling of general well-being.<br \/>\nNext to the dance, there is time to enjoy a real holiday relaxation: in P\u00e4rnu there is the sea, with wide sandy beaches and secluded beaches, boulevards and parks to go walking and cycling (bike rental is everywhere and cheap), and take care of your wellness area with Finnish sauna, turkish bath, hot and cold water pools, Japanese bath and jacuzzi available to us for free at the hotel and the opportunity to undergo a wide variety of spa treatments, therapeutic and beauty massages at a very very low cost.<br \/>\nThe town is very pleasant, walk in the center full of cozy cafes, restaurants and excellent shops, makes us feel on holiday: Parnu is in fact a place well known to the northern Europeans because of its beaches and spas .<br \/>\nThe dance course is very intensive in terms of movement and the results in terms of improvement in dance and movement are evident.<br \/>\nHuman experience is also very rich and full, and all accompanied by sun, sea, rest, and good company it feels really renewed!<\/p>\n<p>The organization, according to \u00a0Tanssiva Aurinko and Helena Metsa&#8217;s directions, provides transportation by ferry boat from the port of Helsinki to Tallinn, transport by bus from the port of Tallinn just in front of\u00a0the main door of Viiking Hotel, the free and open use of the luxorious spa area (saunas, steam rooms, swimming pool, and whirlpools) the hotel provides rich buffet for\u00a0breakfast 8included in the package.<br \/>\nThe hotel offers a huge amount of \u00a0beauty treatments: to book them,\u00a0contact the hotel directly (it is recommended to do so in advance by mail, in English, to be sure to have the possibility\u00a0to enjoy the sessions required).<br \/>\nParticipants must reach the port of Tallinn or\u00a0Helsinki according to a specific time table that will be\u00a0specified at the time of enrollment, organize their lunches and dinners and treatments at the beauty and healing centers. For lunch the Hotel provides\u00a0a cheap and good buffet. The village is full of nice, cheap and rich restaurants where you can choose every kind of international menues.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44\" style=\"width: 553px\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\"><a href=\"http:\/\/lyricalarabdance.milangotan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2015\/06\/parnu-in-estonia.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox-image-1\" data-rl_title=\"\" data-rl_caption=\"\" title=\"\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-44\" src=\"http:\/\/lyricalarabdance.milangotan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2015\/06\/parnu-in-estonia-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"parnu in estonia\" width=\"543\" height=\"362\" srcset=\"https:\/\/lyricalarabdance.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2015\/06\/parnu-in-estonia-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/lyricalarabdance.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2015\/06\/parnu-in-estonia.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 543px) 100vw, 543px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-44\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Parnu in Estonia<\/p><\/div>\n<p>All classes are taught entirely in English, and the group is international, so the lingua franca is English. Maybe the summer internship can\u00a0become also an opportunity to learn or brush up your knowledge of the language! If English is not your thing, do not worry: when you share the desire to dance, you understand too! You can be helped in translation by many students and the teacher herself.<\/p>\n<p>An opportunity not to be missed!<br \/>\nFor registration and information<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Signing up to the workshop and inquiries about the trip by email:\u00a0<\/span><a href=\"mailto:mari.poikkilinja@saunalahti.fi\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">mari.poikkilinja@saunalahti.fi<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When signing up to the workshop, you will get detailed information for\u00a0travel booking (reservation number etc).\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Inquiries about the workshop:\u00a0<\/span><a href=\"mailto:sabina.todaro@hotmail.it\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">sabina.todaro@hotmail.it<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Inquiries about the trip:\u00a0<\/span><a href=\"mailto:gaotina@mbnet.fi\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">gaotina@mbnet.fi<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Lyrical Arab Dance residential summer workshop from July, 27th\/31th 2018 Join Sabina Todaro\u2019s Lyrical Arab dance workshop in P\u00e4rnu, Estonia. In P\u00e4rnu you can find both the seaside (with a beautiful sandy beach) and&#46;&#46;&#46;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":33,"comment_status":"closed","pin